# 🚀 AI Productivity Toolkit

A lightweight AI-inspired web app that helps users:
- Summarize text
- Rewrite content
- Generate ideas instantly

## ✨ Features
- Clean and simple UI
- Fast client-side processing
- Easy to extend with real AI APIs (OpenAI, etc.)

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## 📌 Future Improvements
- Integrate real AI APIs
- Add authentication
- Export results

